                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": "Figure 1. An approximate schematic of gravito-acoustic wave emission and propagation inside and near the PNS. Gravity waves (dashed) are generated by the convective region, attenuate in the evanescent region, and re-emerge as acoustic waves (solid) near the surface of the PNS. They then propagate outward through the wind until they form shocks and dissipate. The region of possible shock formation and heat deposition overlaps with the "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                171,
                                                1170,
                                                1190,
                                                1502
                                            ],
                                            "type": "inline_equation",
                                            "content": "\\alpha"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                171,
                                                1170,
                                                1190,
                                                1502
                                            ],
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": "-forming region. If the waves shock before or during "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                171,
                                                1170,
                                                1190,
                                                1502
                                            ],
                                            "type": "inline_equation",
                                            "content": "\\alpha"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                171,
                                                1170,
                                                1190,
                                                1502
                                            ],
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": " recombination, the additional heating will inhibit seed formation, making a strong r-process more likely."
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
