                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "(Pons et al. 1999). The atmosphere of the PNS is nearly isothermal due to neutrino interactions (e.g. Qian & Woosley 1996) which results in a Brunt- Vaisala frequency, "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\omega_{BV}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ", that is slowly varying with radius up to the point at which the wind is launched. Based on the models described in section 5.1 and the models of Roberts & Reddy (2017), "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\omega_{BV} \\sim 5 \\times 10^{4} \\mathrm{s}^{- 1}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". The Lamb frequency in this region is "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\omega_{L} \\sim c_{s} / r \\sim 10^{3} \\mathrm{s}^{- 1}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        171,
                                        1590,
                                        1190,
                                        2001
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". Therefore, the waves excited by convection will be evanescent through the PNS atmosphere and emerge into the acoustic branch as the density rapidly falls off in the wind region."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
